Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.spl.data.readers

Classes for storing and reading data samples and computations of statistics from them.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataReader
    Provides unified interface to read measured data.
    RevisionReader
    Provides unified interface to read data revision from files.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JmhJsonRevisionReader
    Reader for new JSON format of JMH generated data.
    JmhJsonRevisionReader.RevisionFactory  
    LineOrientedRevisionReader
    Reader for text files with one integer number per line.
    LineOrientedRevisionReader.RevisionFactory  
    NumbersOnlyRevisionReader
    Reader for text files with one integer number per line.
    NumbersOnlyRevisionReader.RevisionFactory  
    PlainDataReader<T extends RevisionReader>
    Data reader from plain text formats.
    StructuredDataReader<T extends RevisionReader>
    Data reader from formats like JMH JSON.

    DataReader.ReaderException
    Exception indicating error when reading data.
